thread.title: BRIEF-Locindus FY Consolidated Net Profit Up at ‍9.5​ Million Euros

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Locindus FY Consolidated Net Profit Up at ‍9.5​ Million Euros
text:
March 9 (Reuters) - LOCINDUS SA:
* FY CONSOLIDATED NET PROFIT EUR ‍9.5​ MILLION VERSUS EUR 6.8 MILLION YEAR AGO
* PROPOSED DIVIDEND FOR 2017 IS EUR 0.89 PER SHARE * FY GROSS OPERATING PROFIT EUR ‍13.0​ MILLION VERSUS EUR 9.7 MILLION YEAR AGO
* FY NET BANKING INCOME EUR ‍18.2​ MILLION VERSUS EUR 15.1 MILLION YEAR AGO
* FY 2018 FINANCIAL TARGETS ARE COMPARABLE TO THOSE OF THE PREVIOUS YEAR
* FY COST OF RISK EUR ‍+0.1​ MILLION VERSUS EUR -0.1 MILLION YEAR AGO Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
